<p>Seamless and luxurious air travel.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <div class=\"service-info\">\n                        <h4>Concierge Assistance</h4>\n                        <p>24/7 support for your peace of mind.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                 <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <div class=\"service-info\">\n                        <h4>Luxury Accommodations</h4>\n                        <p>Handpicked hotels and private villas.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"testimonials\">\n            <h3>What Our Clients Say</h3>\n            <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n                <p>\"Elysian Escapes created the most magical anniversary trip for us. Every detail was perfect!\"</p>\n                <span class=\"author\">- Olivia & James</span>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"contact-form\">\n            <h3>Let's Plan Your Escape</h3>\n            <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Inquiry</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Elysian Escapes. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}